Service-activated document transformers can utilize instances from DI to modify the app. The following sample demonstrates a document transformer that uses the [IAuthenticationSchemeProvider](/en-us/dotnet/api/microsoft.aspnetcore.authentication.iauthenticationschemeprovider) service from the authentication layer. It checks if any JWT bearer-related schemes are registered in the app and adds them to the OpenAPI document's top level:

